    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a great option for someone looking for a reliable project or a budget-friendly daily driver. The exterior shows clear signs of age, including several noticeable scratches, a few small dings on the passenger side, and some fading on the clear coat. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few minor stains, though all electronics and the climate control are currently functioning. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it will likely need a suspension tune-up and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for the price, provided you\u2019re willing to put in a little work to bring it back to its best.",
