    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. With its flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original luster, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class. For the discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection, this represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly distinguished masterpiece.",
      "price": 48900.0,
