      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem! Honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014it's been babied its whole life and is in truly flawless shape. Not a single scratch or smudge to be found, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
