    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman S, presented in concours-ready condition. This mid-engine masterpiece is powered by a 2.5L flat-four featuring Variable Turbine Geometry (VTG)\u2014tech derived from the 911 Turbo\u2014delivering 350hp and 309 lb-ft of torque with virtually zero lag. The drivetrain is anchored by a lightning-quick 7-speed PDK dual-clutch transmission and Porsche Torque Vectoring (PTV) with a mechanical rear differential lock. Chassis dynamics are enhanced by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing a 10mm reduction in ride height and adaptive damping for surgical precision. This vehicle boasts a documented service history, a clean DME over-rev report, and flawless factory paint depth. Mechanically synchronized and aesthetically perfect, it represents the pinnacle of the four-cylinder boxer era.",
